{"tid":1253303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2017-01-15]胡官斥林鄭專權對港好危險：唔可以畀佢當選","createTime":"2019-06-23T13:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:25:45.000Z","uid":47132,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a65c686bc3f47e641a04ba5e9416f2bf90e168c5","tid":1253303,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/14220415/image1489500227464.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F14220415%2Fimage1489500227464.png&h=dd2f5843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚舉行的特首選舉論壇，第三節討論民生政策。候選人胡國興於互相質詢環節，再次批評林鄭月娥在西九故宮館事件上「自把自為」，將己見加諸香港市民，所做的諮詢其實是「假諮詢」。林鄭反駁時，強調自己著重「公眾參與」。<br />\n<br />\n胡國興直言林鄭「要諮詢嘅嘢唔去諮詢，剩係話我已經為你哋啲人諗好咗嘞&hellip;&hellip;所有專權嘅人都係講呢啲嘢嘅，所以我覺得（林鄭上台）對香港係好危險」，即獲不少人鼓掌歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n胡官續指，相信港人和選委的眼睛雪亮，「咁嘅人（林鄭）呢，你唔可以畀佢做特首，管理香港嘅事務，因為好危險，每一件事都係替你決定，唔需要你再諗啦」。胡世全則未有正面評價林鄭，指梁振英所作所為有目共睹，負責任的政府政策應透明公開。<br />\n<br />\n不過，前立法會主席、民建聯創黨主席曾鈺成在西九故官館爭議之初，便已批評分享了由其擔任召集人之香港願景的短片，指出「公眾諮詢」與「公眾參與」的分別，並藉此暗批林鄭在事件上所進行的是「假諮詢」。"},{"pid":"bc374539dced1c83d05c45ec6af990aa606b8148","tid":1253303,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cef7755025ca84ce2ee4ab971835105fb2e140","tid":1253303,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e80ae9a538da118bea79d218ccc524457512781","tid":1253303,"uid":265467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"家有一老...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6d8e81b11eba6aa40e4ecfa6390f361f067344","tid":1253303,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"要諮詢嘅嘢唔去諮詢，剩係話我已經為你哋啲人諗好咗嘞&hellip;&hellip;所有專權嘅人都係講呢啲嘢嘅，所以我覺得（林鄭上台）對香港係好危險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1653a58facdc08301da64846ceea1b2e1ddab2fd","tid":1253303,"uid":185045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}